        "at": "2026-07-18T13:22:54"
      }
    },
    {
      "beat_id": "B11",
      "estimated_duration_s": 12,
      "narration_text": "Why does the energy ladder climb in equal steps? Because the Hamiltonian factorizes into operators whose action changes the energy by one fixed quantum. The same mathematical idea later becomes creation and annihilation of field quanta.",
      "shot": {
        "type": "CARD",
        "source": "own",
